snippet.textDisplay: On my repeats. I am hindu and found so many similarities between hindu bhajan and this song. The soul of the song is same, religion can be any. Also, there is whole urdu bunch at the end of the song... Al mustafa... I don't understand any word of it but that's favourite part of the song. This leads me to believe that all kinds of religions are connected up there. We are so small to point out differences.
